## Strategic Vision

The project's most significant contribution is not a collection of Cantonese-themed decorations, but the creation of a new ornamental tradition whose decorative grammar emerges from Chinese writing itself.

Where European manuscript ornament evolved from vines, knots, and Christian iconography, a Cantonese ornament package can evolve from radicals, strokes, seals, architectural geometry, and maritime culture.

This would make `cantoneseornament` not merely a regional styling package, but a genuinely new typographic and decorative system.
